  "instructions": "1. Mix red wine, brandy, triple sec, lemonade concentrate, orange juice, lemon juice, and sugar (optional) together in a bowl.\n\n2. Add orange, lemon, and lime slices, and maraschino cherries.\n\n3. Serve immediately over ice, or refrigerate for 8 hours to overnight for best flavor.\n\n4. For a fizzy sangria, add carbonated water just before serving.",
